# Dart Tooling — Prefer MCP Server

When working with Dart/Flutter code, prefer the Dart MCP server tools over grep/find:

- Use `dart > lsp` for symbol resolution, hover docs, and signature help
- Use `dart > analyze_files` for diagnostics instead of `dart analyze` via shell
- Use `dart > pub` / `dart > pub_dev_search` for dependency management
- Use `dart > rip_grep_packages` to search inside package dependencies
- Use `dart > read_package_uris` to explore package source code
- Only fall back to grep/find when searching for patterns the LSP can't express (string literals, comments, TODOs)
